thread.title_full: Cambridge Proofreading reviewed by Martin Franke

author: Martin Franke
title: Martin Franke
text:
I submitted my dissertation for proofreading and received really good suggestions for word choice, grammar, flow and consistency. It was easy to review and implement the changes. I learned a lot and it's now nice to read.
I will for sure come back to your service. Thanks!
Martin
